Make a batter by beating the egg with the flour.  Add a little milk if it is too thick.Dip the ham in the batter.Pan-fry the ham in the oil for one to two minutes either side until crisp.Remove the stems from the mushrooms.Stuff the mushrooms with the parmesan and drizzle with honey.Bake in a hot oven for five to six minutes.Season and serve the mushroom and ham on a bed of rocket.